00:01:34,480 --> 00:01:37,159
(Episode 21)

4
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:42,120
You're at a crossroads in life...

5
00:01:42,359 --> 00:01:44,439
and you have two choices before you.

6
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:46,239
One of them is a flat road...

7
00:01:46,439 --> 00:01:47,799
while another is a bumpy road.

8
00:01:48,719 --> 00:01:51,040
In the end, death is the direction they take.

9
00:01:52,319 --> 00:01:54,280
You hesitated for a long time at the junction,

10
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:55,640
not knowing what to do.

11
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,959
That's why you are seeking help from me.

12
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:59,840
I'm telling you.

13
00:02:01,519 --> 00:02:03,200
If this was back in the day...

14
00:02:04,239 --> 00:02:06,959
I would choose the smooth road.

15
00:02:07,359 --> 00:02:11,960
I really enjoy living a carefree life every day.

16
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:13,599
I'm relaxed and happy.

17
00:02:13,599 --> 00:02:14,840
There's no pressure...

18
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:16,599
- and I don't have to think much. - I know.

19
00:02:16,599 --> 00:02:17,879
But...

20
00:02:18,639 --> 00:02:19,639
recently,

21
00:02:19,639 --> 00:02:22,560
I have a new sentiment about my life.

22
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:23,919
I think...

23
00:02:24,199 --> 00:02:26,879
people should live a more fruitful life.

24
00:02:27,439 --> 00:02:29,479
We have to go through more ups and downs.

25
00:02:29,479 --> 00:02:32,090
We should encounter different things.

26
00:02:32,090 --> 00:02:35,280
We should let different colors fill up our lives.

27
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:38,000
We should enrich our lives with different flavors.

28
00:02:38,159 --> 00:02:39,560
That way, our lives...

29
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:41,319
will be more meaningful.

30
00:02:41,719 --> 00:02:43,960
But your life will surely be a lot more tiring that way.

31
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:45,520
Everything you do is tiring.

32
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:49,479
But every day, on this rough and rugged road,

33
00:02:49,639 --> 00:02:51,199
you'll meet different people...

34
00:02:51,319 --> 00:02:52,879
and different things.

35
00:02:52,879 --> 00:02:54,360
You'll be fooled by a lot of different things...

36
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,719
and get beat up.

37
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:58,759
But these things will all turn into your scales...

38
00:02:58,759 --> 00:03:00,240
and your armor.

39
00:03:00,639 --> 00:03:02,240
They will enrich your life...

40
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:04,000
and allow yourself...

41
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,719
to grow stronger in the future.

42
00:03:05,919 --> 00:03:08,840
These experiences will make your life...

43
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:10,439
very interesting.

44
00:03:11,159 --> 00:03:13,879
People especially like those who are interesting.

45
00:03:13,879 --> 00:03:15,639
Do you want to be liked?

46
00:03:15,759 --> 00:03:17,120
No.

47
00:03:17,479 --> 00:03:18,479
That's because when I'm tired,

48
00:03:18,479 --> 00:03:19,879
all I want to do is eat and sleep.

49
00:03:19,879 --> 00:03:21,719
I don't want to do anything or think about anything.

50
00:03:21,719 --> 00:03:23,080
How relaxing is that?

51
00:03:24,479 --> 00:03:25,840
But...

52
00:03:26,439 --> 00:03:30,680
I think if I were to really live a life like that,

53
00:03:32,159 --> 00:03:34,080
then I may end up envying...

54
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:36,759
those who are busy, always running around,

55
00:03:36,759 --> 00:03:38,560
and have a lot to do.

56
00:03:39,319 --> 00:03:41,039
People are always so indecisive, aren't they?

57
00:03:41,039 --> 00:03:43,319
Yes. People are like that.

58
00:03:44,199 --> 00:03:46,080
You want to take a vacation when you go to school.

59
00:03:46,479 --> 00:03:48,560
When you're on vacation, you want to go to school.

60
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:50,759
When you're working every day, you want to rest.

61
00:03:50,759 --> 00:03:52,719
But you want to start working as soon as you take a break.

62
00:03:52,719 --> 00:03:53,960
Everyone is like that.

63
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,680
I understand.

64
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,719
So you're saying...

65
00:03:58,719 --> 00:04:00,159
people should live a more fruitful, exciting,

66
00:04:00,159 --> 00:04:01,520
and meaningful life, right?

67
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:03,000
Torture yourself.

68
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:07,759
I think your presence...

69
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,879
is already torturing enough.

70
00:04:09,879 --> 00:04:11,479
It's also fruitful and exciting enough.

71
00:04:11,479 --> 00:04:12,919
Let's sleep.

72
00:04:14,319 --> 00:04:15,319
Sleep.

73
00:04:15,319 --> 00:04:17,120
- Are we not talking anymore? - No.

74
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,730
I was just getting fired up.

75
00:04:19,879 --> 00:04:23,050
I hope my nagging today...

76
00:04:23,050 --> 00:04:24,079
brought a bit of help...

77
00:04:24,079 --> 00:04:25,800
to your path of life.

78
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:27,920
I'm going.

79
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:29,879
Good night.

80
00:04:35,759 --> 00:04:37,000
Thank you.

81
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,240
Sleep tight.

82
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:31,399
Mr. Sheng, are you looking for Mr. Hou...

83
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,879
Go and open the door for me.

84
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,720
Mr. Sheng, are you all right?

85
00:05:41,839 --> 00:05:43,160
Is it swollen?

86
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:44,399
No.

87
00:05:45,319 --> 00:05:46,680
- What about my hairstyle? - It's fine.

88
00:05:47,519 --> 00:05:49,000
Go and open the door.

89
00:06:02,879 --> 00:06:04,000
- Mr. Sheng, please wait. - Shut up.

90
00:06:09,519 --> 00:06:10,759
Mr. Sheng.

91
00:06:11,199 --> 00:06:12,439
This...

92
00:06:12,959 --> 00:06:15,480
What brings you here?

93
00:06:17,439 --> 00:06:19,000
From the look of it,

94
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:22,480
it seems like you're here to interrogate me.

95
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:25,519
Did I do something wrong that upsets you?

96
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:31,160
Stop talking about useless things.

97
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:34,759
We've worked together for so many years.

98
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:37,519
We've had arguments and got angry at each other.

99
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:41,439
But luckily, we both have straightforward personalities.

100
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:45,000
We're fine after we talk things out and put things behind us.

101
00:06:45,959 --> 00:06:51,480
That's why our relationship has lasted until today.

102
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,959
Am I right?

103
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:55,439
That's right, Mr. Sheng.

104
00:06:56,319 --> 00:07:00,279
You're suddenly saying all these things. It's making me...

105
00:07:00,839 --> 00:07:02,480
What's going on?

106
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:05,160
Did someone upset you or something?

107
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:10,639
Honestly, this matter is quite humiliating.

108
00:07:10,879 --> 00:07:12,680
Originally, our kids...

109
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:15,519
should be handling matters by themselves.

110
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,480
Am I right?

111
00:07:17,959 --> 00:07:20,560
But my kid is a girl.

112
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:22,279
So...

113
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:26,680
So I'm taking advantage of this to complain a little.

114
00:07:26,959 --> 00:07:28,439
My dear friend,

115
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:31,079
you have been helping me all these years.

116
00:07:31,199 --> 00:07:33,319
How are you taking advantage of me?

117
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,680
Did Hou Jue...

118
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:37,560
make Chen Chen angry?

119
00:07:38,319 --> 00:07:39,920
Is that right, my friend?

120
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:44,240
Initially, our plan was...

121
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:46,600
if they can be together,

122
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:48,279
then the two of us...

123
00:07:48,519 --> 00:07:52,319
can take our business relationship a step further.

124
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:54,120
We'll become relatives.

125
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,519
Am I right?

126
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,839
You're absolutely right.

127
00:07:57,839 --> 00:08:00,120
This is a good thing.

128
00:08:00,279 --> 00:08:01,879
- Yes. - That's right.

129
00:08:01,879 --> 00:08:03,199
If they're not meant to be,

130
00:08:03,199 --> 00:08:05,600
we can just let this go...

131
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:07,879
and can keep doing our business.

132
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:11,639
After all, this is just our wishful thinking.

133
00:08:11,639 --> 00:08:12,720
Isn't that right?

134
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:14,439
That's right.

135
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:18,279
If he doesn't like Chen Chen,

136
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:21,480
that's okay.

137
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,519
I had her at an old age.

138
00:08:25,439 --> 00:08:28,319
My child has always been spoiled,

139
00:08:28,319 --> 00:08:30,199
so she has a lot of bad habits.

140
00:08:31,439 --> 00:08:33,039
But even so,

141
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:36,720
there are several handsome and successful young men...

142
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:38,360
lining up to pursue her.

143
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:40,600
- Do you believe that? - I do.

144
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:43,210
Mr. Sheng, honestly, I even think...

145
00:08:43,679 --> 00:08:47,480
Chen Chen is a bit out of Hou Jue's league.

146
00:08:48,399 --> 00:08:49,960
That's how I truly feel.

147
00:08:50,090 --> 00:08:51,759
But I don't understand.

148
00:08:51,879 --> 00:08:54,279
I didn't hear Hou Jue mention...

149
00:08:54,450 --> 00:08:58,039
how he angered Chen Chen either.

150
00:08:58,279 --> 00:08:59,759
How?

151
00:09:00,039 --> 00:09:01,519
If I tell you,

152
00:09:01,639 --> 00:09:03,120
you'll feel humiliated too.

153
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,879
Tell me.

154
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:08,720
Your son sure is something.

155
00:09:09,279 --> 00:09:12,330
Not only did he not protect Chen Chen,

156
00:09:12,679 --> 00:09:15,519
but he even sided with that female bodyguard instead.

157
00:09:15,639 --> 00:09:18,090
He even scolded Chen Chen...

158
00:09:18,330 --> 00:09:20,879
in front of so many people.

159
00:09:21,279 --> 00:09:23,559
I can't accept this.

160
00:09:23,919 --> 00:09:25,720
That jerk!

161
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,450
I'm so mad.

162
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:30,240
How could he do such a thing?

163
00:09:32,330 --> 00:09:35,240
Even I'm mad just hearing about it, let alone you.

164
00:09:35,399 --> 00:09:36,759
I'm serious.

165
00:09:37,159 --> 00:09:38,159
Mr. Sheng.

166
00:09:40,559 --> 00:09:42,039
Mr. Sheng.

167
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:44,840
Calm down first.

168
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:47,330
On behalf of Hou Jue,

169
00:09:47,330 --> 00:09:51,330
I apologize to you and Chen Chen.

170
00:09:51,330 --> 00:09:52,919
I sincerely apologize.

171
00:09:53,039 --> 00:09:54,519
It's Hou Jue's problem.

172
00:09:54,519 --> 00:09:57,039
I'll definitely teach him a lesson later.

173
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:02,210
Regarding your apology,

174
00:10:02,559 --> 00:10:04,840
I'll reluctantly accept it.

175
00:10:06,159 --> 00:10:08,210
But for my daughter,

176
00:10:08,210 --> 00:10:09,720
I can't let go of this.

177
00:10:11,159 --> 00:10:12,559
You're right.

178
00:10:12,559 --> 00:10:13,840
I know.

179
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:16,759
Chen Chen is your precious daughter.

180
00:10:16,759 --> 00:10:19,279
Never mind you, even I can't stand it...

181
00:10:19,279 --> 00:10:20,799
after hearing this.

182
00:10:20,799 --> 00:10:23,210
Whoever upsets Chen Chen...

183
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:25,330
is going against you.

184
00:10:26,330 --> 00:10:27,919
How about this, Mr. Sheng?

185
00:10:28,639 --> 00:10:29,840
Please calm down first.

186
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,559
Later on, come to my clubhouse.

187
00:10:31,679 --> 00:10:33,000
I'll arrange it.

188
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,840
Bring Chen Chen over.

189
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:38,000
I'll bring that punk...

190
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,960
and make him apologize to Chen Chen...

191
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,600
in front of both of you.

192
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:46,000
You can do whatever you want with him then.

193
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,879
Does that sound good?

194
00:10:49,039 --> 00:10:50,679
What about that female bodyguard?

195
00:10:52,159 --> 00:10:53,639
That's easy.

196
00:10:53,639 --> 00:10:54,879
It's a small matter.

197
00:10:54,879 --> 00:10:57,000
I'll just let her go.

198
00:10:57,480 --> 00:10:59,759
What do you say, old friend?

199
00:11:03,919 --> 00:11:05,200
Brew me some tea.

200
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:07,000
Okay, I'll brew some tea.

201
00:11:12,919 --> 00:11:15,480
The interior design of your company...

202
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:17,279
really doesn't make sense.

203
00:11:21,879 --> 00:11:23,120
Hello.

204
00:11:24,519 --> 00:11:26,120
Okay, I got it.

205
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:39,200
Mr. Hou wants to see me. I'm going over there.

206
00:11:42,799 --> 00:11:44,639
It must be about that stupid matter with Chen Chen.

207
00:11:45,919 --> 00:11:47,279
I don't know.

208
00:11:47,399 --> 00:11:49,360
- I'll go with you. - It's okay.

209
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:50,799
He told me to go alone. He didn't ask for you.

210
00:11:50,799 --> 00:11:51,879
It's okay.

211
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:54,720
I'll be your bodyguard today. Come on.

212
00:12:01,399 --> 00:12:03,120
Mr. Hou Junior, Mr. Hou...

213
00:12:04,799 --> 00:12:05,919
- Wait for me at the door. - Come in.

214
00:12:10,559 --> 00:12:12,039
Mr. Hou, did you ask for me?

215
00:12:12,679 --> 00:12:14,039
Have a seat.

216
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:18,600
Shi Yi.

217
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:22,039
You've been with the company...

218
00:12:22,399 --> 00:12:24,080
for almost two months now, right?

219
00:12:24,279 --> 00:12:25,759
Although there were ups and downs...

220
00:12:25,759 --> 00:12:27,080
and you experienced several obstacles,

221
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:28,799
no matter what happens,

222
00:12:28,799 --> 00:12:30,720
you've always fulfilled your duty...

223
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:33,159
and done your job well.

224
00:12:33,159 --> 00:12:36,120
As your client, I'm very satisfied with that.

225
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:37,960
Thank you, Mr. Hou.

226
00:12:39,039 --> 00:12:42,120
Back then, I recruited a female bodyguard for Hou Jue...

227
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:45,480
because I like how they're composed and meticulous.

228
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:48,000
Not only do you have to keep him safe,

229
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:50,240
at the same time, you must also restrain his behavior...

230
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:52,120
and not let him stir up trouble.

231
00:12:52,799 --> 00:12:54,679
However, it seems like...

232
00:12:54,679 --> 00:12:58,039
I was too simpleminded.

233
00:12:59,080 --> 00:13:01,120
Having a single man and woman...

234
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:04,360
spend 24 hours a day together...

235
00:13:04,559 --> 00:13:09,240
is bound to trigger some chemistry.

236
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:11,480
Actually, I can understand that.

237
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:13,360
Even if you're raising a pet,

238
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:15,120
feelings will grow as time goes by,

239
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,840
let alone two people.

240
00:13:18,559 --> 00:13:21,080
Our company has a very specific rule about that.

241
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:22,840
We can't date our employers.

242
00:13:23,039 --> 00:13:25,240
I'll strictly abide by it. Don't worry.

243
00:13:29,279 --> 00:13:31,200
I don't care if you date or not.

244
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:32,720
