00:25:43,960 --> 00:25:45,680
- Let's go, ma'am. Come on. - There's really no need.

484
00:25:45,680 --> 00:25:47,160
What are you guys doing?

485
00:25:47,920 --> 00:25:49,960
- He came to buy... - I just took Shi Yi shopping.

486
00:25:51,960 --> 00:25:53,440
We just bought a purse.

487
00:25:54,519 --> 00:25:55,519
Something urgent came up.

488
00:25:55,519 --> 00:25:57,480
I'll get going now, ma'am and Mr. Wu.

489
00:25:57,799 --> 00:25:59,160
- All right. - Let's go.

490
00:25:59,440 --> 00:26:00,599
- I'm leaving then. - Shi Yi.

491
00:26:00,599 --> 00:26:02,400
- Thank you. - No problem.

492
00:26:02,400 --> 00:26:03,480
I'm leaving.

493
00:26:03,480 --> 00:26:04,960
You...

494
00:26:08,839 --> 00:26:10,720
The conversation was going well. Why did you keep trying to explain?

495
00:26:10,720 --> 00:26:12,039
Why do you always ruin things for me?

496
00:26:12,039 --> 00:26:13,119
What did I do?

497
00:26:13,119 --> 00:26:14,319
You didn't even let me talk.

498
00:26:14,319 --> 00:26:15,480
You're the one to talk.

499
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:16,640
What nonsense were you saying just now?

500
00:26:16,640 --> 00:26:17,799
Anyhow, you're not allowed to explain to them.

501
00:26:17,799 --> 00:26:19,039
Who are you to tell me what to do?

502
00:26:19,039 --> 00:26:20,160
What do you mean?

503
00:26:20,160 --> 00:26:21,640
Who does he think he is?

504
00:26:21,640 --> 00:26:22,640
He's trying to get in with your parents...

505
00:26:22,640 --> 00:26:23,920
while I'm not looking.

506
00:26:23,920 --> 00:26:25,839
I hate people like that. He's so cunning.

507
00:26:25,839 --> 00:26:27,359
You need to stay away from this kind of person.

508
00:26:27,359 --> 00:26:29,640
He already knew my parents very well over 10 years ago.

509
00:26:29,640 --> 00:26:31,920
So what? Can he do this just because he knows them well?

510
00:26:31,920 --> 00:26:33,720
He pretends not to do anything, but he's secretly making moves.

511
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:35,359
What kind of behavior is that?

512
00:26:35,599 --> 00:26:36,839
How can he do that?

513
00:26:37,799 --> 00:26:39,160
Say something.

514
00:26:40,240 --> 00:26:41,720
Why are you looking at me?

515
00:26:42,880 --> 00:26:44,359
What kind of behavior is that?

516
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:03,480
What's wrong, Ms. Zhang and Mr. Wu?

517
00:27:05,039 --> 00:27:06,799
If you think...

518
00:27:06,960 --> 00:27:09,400
I'm bothered by Mr. Hou giving Shi Yi a gift,

519
00:27:09,400 --> 00:27:10,839
then you're overthinking it.

520
00:27:11,079 --> 00:27:13,119
That purse is really expensive.

521
00:27:13,319 --> 00:27:14,359
From what I know about Shi Yi,

522
00:27:14,359 --> 00:27:15,880
she would never accept it.

523
00:27:15,880 --> 00:27:17,880
- That's right. - That's for sure.

524
00:27:18,400 --> 00:27:21,039
Besides, we're different.

525
00:27:21,200 --> 00:27:22,279
When I met Shi Yi,

526
00:27:22,279 --> 00:27:23,480
she was still in elementary school, right?

527
00:27:23,480 --> 00:27:24,480
Yes.

528
00:27:24,640 --> 00:27:26,039
She has always had many pursuers ever since she was young.

529
00:27:26,039 --> 00:27:27,440
I'm used to it now.

530
00:27:27,440 --> 00:27:28,440
That's right.

531
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:30,720
But Shi Yi is very faithful.

532
00:27:32,440 --> 00:27:33,559
Mr. Wu and Ms. Zhang.

533
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:36,839
My parents passed away early.

534
00:27:37,839 --> 00:27:39,200
So...

535
00:27:39,519 --> 00:27:41,119
deep down,

536
00:27:41,240 --> 00:27:42,599
I've always thought of you two...

537
00:27:42,920 --> 00:27:44,279
as my parents.

538
00:27:45,799 --> 00:27:47,160
Shi Yi is busy.

539
00:27:47,680 --> 00:27:49,079
I'll take care of you on her behalf.

540
00:27:50,319 --> 00:27:51,480
Lan Qi.

541
00:27:51,880 --> 00:27:54,400
Hearing you say that, I feel...

542
00:27:57,559 --> 00:27:59,000
You're a good kid.

543
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:00,880
All right, let's go eat.

544
00:28:01,000 --> 00:28:02,000
Okay.

545
00:28:08,000 --> 00:28:10,440
Lan Qi said that purse is quite expensive.

546
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:12,279
If Shi Yi doesn't accept it, it'll be such a waste.

547
00:28:12,279 --> 00:28:13,599
She can give it to me.

548
00:28:13,599 --> 00:28:15,960
It could sell for a lot of money on secondhand shopping websites.

549
00:28:15,960 --> 00:28:17,119
How cheap.

550
00:28:17,279 --> 00:28:18,400
Look at you.

551
00:28:18,640 --> 00:28:20,559
I was just kidding, but you took it seriously.

552
00:28:20,880 --> 00:28:22,000
You're so old now,

553
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:23,319
yet you still have no sense of humor.

554
00:28:23,319 --> 00:28:24,440
Whatever.

555
00:28:26,119 --> 00:28:27,160
I'm just wondering...

556
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:29,039
what stage he and Shi Yi are at now.

557
00:28:29,319 --> 00:28:30,480
Why don't you send her a message and ask?

558
00:28:30,480 --> 00:28:31,519
There's no point in asking.

559
00:28:31,519 --> 00:28:33,839
She'll definitely say they're just working together.

560
00:28:34,200 --> 00:28:37,200
But I saw Hou Jue's eyes.

561
00:28:38,079 --> 00:28:39,160
He can't fool me.

562
00:28:40,359 --> 00:28:43,079
If Shi Yi has really fallen in love with Hou Jue,

563
00:28:43,079 --> 00:28:44,240
what should we do then?

564
00:28:44,240 --> 00:28:45,480
What about Lan Qi?

565
00:28:45,640 --> 00:28:47,079
That would be a good thing.

566
00:28:47,200 --> 00:28:48,880
Both of them can pursue her at the same time.

567
00:28:49,319 --> 00:28:50,599
If there's a rival,

568
00:28:50,599 --> 00:28:53,039
they'll both care about Shi Yi even more.

569
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:56,640
Moreover, Shi Yi will understand her own value even better.

570
00:28:56,640 --> 00:28:58,000
That's right.

571
00:28:58,160 --> 00:28:59,920
In terms of competitive mechanisms,

572
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:01,480
you're an expert.

573
00:29:01,480 --> 00:29:05,279
Back then, I also had to fight my way through a rain of bullets...

574
00:29:05,279 --> 00:29:08,440
and a bloodbath.

575
00:29:12,839 --> 00:29:15,079
Why did I marry you?

576
00:29:18,160 --> 00:29:19,799
Why did you follow me here?

577
00:29:20,640 --> 00:29:21,640
Aren't you going to take me home?

578
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:22,880
Who said I would do that?

579
00:29:23,119 --> 00:29:24,759
Your place is so close. Walk home by yourself.

580
00:29:25,000 --> 00:29:26,240
I have a date.

581
00:29:36,039 --> 00:29:38,079
Isn't this a competitive mechanism?

582
00:29:54,519 --> 00:29:57,599
Give me your parents' phone numbers.

583
00:29:57,599 --> 00:29:58,839
Why?

584
00:30:01,279 --> 00:30:04,000
You're with me every day, right?

585
00:30:04,480 --> 00:30:08,519
You risk your life for me, right?

586
00:30:08,519 --> 00:30:10,279
If anything happens to you,

587
00:30:10,279 --> 00:30:11,720
as your boss,

588
00:30:11,720 --> 00:30:13,920
I have to tell your parents right away.

589
00:30:14,799 --> 00:30:15,799
It's okay.

590
00:30:15,799 --> 00:30:18,599
If anything happens to me, you can notify our company.

591
00:30:18,599 --> 00:30:20,160
They'll notify my parents.

592
00:30:20,160 --> 00:30:22,240
A notification from your company is one thing.

593
00:30:22,240 --> 00:30:25,319
Right? It's completely different if it comes from me.

594
00:30:25,559 --> 00:30:27,119
I have to tell your parents directly.

595
00:30:27,119 --> 00:30:28,599
That shows sincerity.

596
00:30:29,079 --> 00:30:30,960
- People... - That's enough.

597
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:32,960
Stop thinking about these useless things.

598
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:35,119
Hurry and think about how to apologize to Chen Chen...

599
00:30:35,119 --> 00:30:36,799
when you get to the restaurant later.

600
00:30:36,799 --> 00:30:38,720
Why should I apologize? I'm not apologizing.

601
00:30:38,720 --> 00:30:40,160
I'm asking for phone numbers right now.

602
00:30:40,279 --> 00:30:42,799
I'll develop a good relationship with your parents first.

603
00:30:42,799 --> 00:30:44,160
That way,

604
00:30:44,279 --> 00:30:46,440
this can slowly develop as normal...

605
00:30:46,440 --> 00:30:48,000
You're not getting their numbers.

606
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:20,240
Has that Little Qi of yours...

607
00:31:20,400 --> 00:31:21,640
not contacted you yet?

608
00:31:21,640 --> 00:31:22,720
No.

609
00:31:23,119 --> 00:31:24,680
He hasn't done anything at all.

610
00:31:25,680 --> 00:31:27,519
This guy is strange.

611
00:31:28,359 --> 00:31:29,960
Is he that calm?

612
00:31:30,799 --> 00:31:32,119
He's deep.

613
00:31:32,119 --> 00:31:33,359
That's true.

614
00:31:33,480 --> 00:31:35,519
Anyone is deeper than you.

615
00:31:37,240 --> 00:31:38,480
All right.

616
00:31:38,759 --> 00:31:40,279
I'll wait for you here.

617
00:31:40,279 --> 00:31:41,519
Go in.

618
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:44,839
Remember.

619
00:31:44,839 --> 00:31:46,079
Be patient.

620
00:31:46,440 --> 00:31:47,880
Think about the bigger picture.

621
00:31:49,880 --> 00:31:51,680
I hope Ms. Chen...

622
00:31:51,680 --> 00:31:53,279
can bring her best today.

623
00:31:53,759 --> 00:31:55,400
Open my dad's eyes...

624
00:31:55,759 --> 00:31:58,160
and let him witness her evilness.

625
00:31:59,440 --> 00:32:00,680
I'm going.

626
00:32:00,680 --> 00:32:01,920
Good luck.

627
00:32:04,279 --> 00:32:05,279
Dad.

628
00:32:05,279 --> 00:32:06,640
Mr. Chen.

629
00:32:08,880 --> 00:32:10,960
Why are you so late?

630
00:32:10,960 --> 00:32:12,079
Look at the time.

631
00:32:12,079 --> 00:32:13,680
What time did I tell you to come?

632
00:32:14,759 --> 00:32:16,599
Hurry up and apologize to Chen Chen.

633
00:32:16,599 --> 00:32:18,440
An apology isn't enough.

634
00:32:18,440 --> 00:32:20,079
I went to buy a purse.

635
00:32:20,640 --> 00:32:23,519
Ms. Chen, please accept it. Here.

636
00:32:28,359 --> 00:32:29,839
Look at this.

637
00:32:31,039 --> 00:32:32,359
He's a smart one.

638
00:32:32,359 --> 00:32:33,880
Accept it. See if it's nice.

639
00:32:33,880 --> 00:32:34,880
If you don't like it,

640
00:32:34,880 --> 00:32:36,599
I'll ask my son to buy you a new one.

641
00:32:36,599 --> 00:32:37,960
I'll go right away.

642
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:42,000
It's all right.

643
00:32:42,480 --> 00:32:43,920
Okay, come on.

644
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:48,640
Son, pick up your glass.

645
00:32:48,640 --> 00:32:50,440
- Here, Mr. Sheng. - Okay.

646
00:32:51,920 --> 00:32:54,200
On behalf of my son,

647
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:58,119
I apologize to you and Chen Chen.

648
00:32:58,119 --> 00:32:59,160
It's nothing.

649
00:32:59,160 --> 00:33:00,880
My son doesn't know any better.

650
00:33:00,880 --> 00:33:02,759
Please forgive him.

651
00:33:02,759 --> 00:33:04,000
What did I do wrong?

652
00:33:08,319 --> 00:33:11,440
You upset her.

653
00:33:11,640 --> 00:33:14,119
It's a man's crime.

654
00:33:14,519 --> 00:33:15,960
Do you understand?

655
00:33:15,960 --> 00:33:18,799
Then I've committed a deadly crime.

656
00:33:18,799 --> 00:33:20,640
I apologize.

657
00:33:22,400 --> 00:33:24,039
- Come on. - I'll apologize to you too.

658
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:29,119
Thank you.

659
00:33:29,440 --> 00:33:31,000
That's right.

660
00:33:40,680 --> 00:33:41,799
Zhi Rong.

661
00:33:43,119 --> 00:33:44,759
Thank you so much.

662
00:33:44,759 --> 00:33:48,039
You had to personally take care...

663
00:33:48,039 --> 00:33:50,119
of a trivial matter like this for our kids.

664
00:33:50,119 --> 00:33:53,680
Mr. Sheng, you're treating me as an outsider by saying that.

665
00:33:53,680 --> 00:33:56,640
Kids are still young and reckless.

666
00:33:57,079 --> 00:33:59,079
It's understandable that they have bad tempers.

667
00:33:59,079 --> 00:34:01,400
In fact, having quarrels will bring them closer together.

668
00:34:01,519 --> 00:34:03,440
Don't you remember the times when we were young?

669
00:34:03,440 --> 00:34:05,720
Didn't we also bicker and argue?

670
00:34:07,160 --> 00:34:08,599
That's right.

671
00:34:08,840 --> 00:34:10,079
Chen Chen.

672
00:34:10,199 --> 00:34:13,400
Back then, when Zhi Rong and I worked together,

673
00:34:13,400 --> 00:34:16,559
we didn't trust each other at all.

674
00:34:16,809 --> 00:34:19,000
We really had a lot of arguments.

675
00:34:19,000 --> 00:34:21,599
Yes, I'm telling you.

676
00:34:21,599 --> 00:34:24,599
When your grandpa stepped down and I joined the company,

677
00:34:24,599 --> 00:34:25,639
I was still young.

678
00:34:25,639 --> 00:34:27,159
I didn't know anything.

679
00:34:27,360 --> 00:34:30,920
It was Mr. Sheng who helped me out a lot...

680
00:34:30,920 --> 00:34:32,239
at the most important stage of my life.

681
00:34:32,239 --> 00:34:34,440
We often slammed tables and threw wine glasses...

682
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:36,639
because of business conflicts.

683
00:34:36,639 --> 00:34:37,880
We've done everything.

684
00:34:37,880 --> 00:34:39,000
- Isn't that right, Mr. Sheng? - Yes.

685
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:40,119
But look at us now.

686
00:34:40,119 --> 00:34:41,679
We're fine.

687
00:34:41,679 --> 00:34:44,289
If fate brings two people together,

688
00:34:44,289 --> 00:34:46,519
you should treasure this relationship.

689
00:34:46,519 --> 00:34:48,769
Mr. Sheng and I both have faith in you two.

690
00:34:49,599 --> 00:34:50,599
All right.

691
00:34:52,199 --> 00:34:55,000
Hou Jue, did your female lackey resign from her post yet?

692
00:34:55,000 --> 00:34:56,239
No.

693
00:34:57,400 --> 00:34:58,639
Little brat.

694
00:34:59,199 --> 00:35:01,119
That's enough. It's in the past now.

695
00:35:01,119 --> 00:35:03,000
There's no need to set yourself against a little girl.

696
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:04,000
That's right.

697
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:05,920
Dad, I'm not setting myself against her.

698
00:35:05,920 --> 00:35:07,960
She's just a little lackey. She's not worth my time.

699
00:35:08,719 --> 00:35:09,840
I just want her to leave.

700
00:35:09,840 --> 00:35:10,960
This...

701
00:35:11,519 --> 00:35:12,880
Chen Chen.

702
00:35:13,329 --> 00:35:14,920
Listen to me.

703
00:35:14,920 --> 00:35:17,119
That girl really can't leave.

704
00:35:17,119 --> 00:35:18,920
I especially hired that girl from a security company...

705
00:35:18,920 --> 00:35:20,769
to protect my son.

706
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:22,559
She used to be an athlete.

707
00:35:22,559 --> 00:35:24,679
She had won championships and medals.

708
00:35:24,679 --> 00:35:27,519
Her working ability is definitely top-notch.

709
00:35:27,519 --> 00:35:29,329
With her by my son's side...

710
00:35:29,329 --> 00:35:30,400
Mr. Sheng, you also know this.

711
00:35:30,400 --> 00:35:31,719
I only have one son.

712
00:35:31,840 --> 00:35:34,519
I'll feel a lot more at ease.

713
00:35:34,519 --> 00:35:35,639
That's true.

714
00:35:35,769 --> 00:35:37,000
Right?

715
00:35:37,289 --> 00:35:38,809
No wonder she's so fierce.

716
00:35:39,440 --> 00:35:41,039
That's more the reason she has to leave.

717
00:35:44,559 --> 00:35:45,809
All right.

718
00:35:46,079 --> 00:35:47,289
But she didn't do anything wrong.

719
00:35:47,289 --> 00:35:48,639
Why does she have to leave?

720
00:35:49,119 --> 00:35:50,480
How was she not wrong?

721
00:35:51,880 --> 00:35:53,960
She bullied me. I hate her! Is that not good enough of a reason?

722
00:35:56,679 --> 00:35:59,289
Chen Chen. That is good enough.

723
00:35:59,289 --> 00:36:00,880
How about this?

724
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:03,440
